flowchart TB
    P1([1.0 User Management])
    P2([2.0 Resume Processing])
    P3([3.0 Career Recommendation Engine])
    P4([4.0 Employability Analysis])
    P5([5.0 Opportunity Matching])

    D1[(User DB)]
    D2[(Resume DB)]
    D3[(Career / Job DB)]
    D4[(Analytics DB)]
    D5[(Opportunity DB)]

    Users((Student / Graduate))

    Users -- "Registration · Credentials" --> P1
    P1 -- "Auth Status · Profile" --> Users
    P1 <--> D1

    Users -- "Uploaded Resume" --> P2
    P2 -- "Extracted Skills · Experience" --> P3
    P2 <--> D2

    P3 -- "Personalized Recommendations" --> Users
    P3 <--> D3

    Users -- "Skills · Certifications · Experience" --> P4
    P4 -- "Employability Score · Skill Gaps" --> Users
    P4 <--> D4

    P3 --> P5
    P5 -- "Internship / Job Recommendations" --> Users
    P5 <--> D5
